name: He loves me, He loves me not Painting
description:
This is an original piece of artwork painted by me, Jennifer Birge. 

12x12 He loves me, He loves me not... 

This whimsical painting was painted using acrylic paints. The sides are red and purple striped to add a more whimsical flare to the overall painting. It is painted on a premade frame. I stretched the canvas myself. Don't worry, I'm a professional. :) Painting will be shipped in a box with lots of bubble wrap to protect it from getting damaged. (invoice included)

**Painting DOES NOT include hanging wire and does not need any, you can hang it right on the nail**

Colors: Blues, Pinks, Purples, browns, Red

Size: 12 wide, 12 inches long, 1 inch depth


Pictures taken with Sony Cyber Shot 7.2 mega pixel - colors may be distorted a wee bit due to lighting. 


You can see more pictures of this painting at: 
www.jenniferbirge.etsy.com

name: Layla Painting
description:
This is an original piece of artwork painted by me, Jennifer Birge. 

I call her Layla! 

This uniquely elegant painting has a feeling of it's own. It was painted using acrylic paints. The canvas wraps around the sides of the wood. It is painted on a handmade wooden frame. I stretched the canvas myself. Don't worry, I'm a professional. :) Layla has white almost translucent flowers painted down the left side of her body. Painting will be shipped in a flat box with lots of bubble wrap to protect it from getting damaged. (invoice included)

**Painting DOES NOT include hanging wire**

Colors: Blues, Blacks, Grays, Whites, Tans

Size: 24 inches wide, 36 inches long, 1 1/2 inch depth


Pictures taken with Sony Cyber Shot 7.2 mega pixel - colors may be distorted a wee bit due to lighting. 


You can see more pictures of this painting at:
www.jenniferbirge.etsy.com
